Hi Alan,

From my point of view, I will hopefully use the data to evaluate the ability of our spatially-explicit (i.e. gridded) coupled model (canal system-land surface-groundwater) to capture the observed groundwater dynamics. Hence it's likely that we will need to use the time series data.

Of course that is dependent on there being adequate data availability in the Gandak - so my first step will be to look at this.


